item.description:
SoftLayer_Billing_Item::cancelItem Cancel a service or resource.
Overview Cancel the resource or service for a billing Item. By default the billing item will be canceled on the next bill date and reclaim of the resource will begin shortly after the cancellation. Setting the &ldquo;cancelImmediately&rdquo; property to true will start the cancellation immediately if the item is eligible to be canceled immediately.
The reason parameter could be from the list below: * &ldquo;No longer needed&rdquo; * &ldquo;Business closing down&rdquo; * &ldquo;Server / Upgrade Costs&rdquo; * &ldquo;Migrating to larger server&rdquo; * &ldquo;Migrating to smaller server&rdquo; * &ldquo;Migrating to a different SoftLayer datacenter&rdquo; * &ldquo;Network performance / latency&rdquo; * &ldquo;Support response / timing&rdquo; * &ldquo;Sales process / upgrades&rdquo; * &ldquo;Moving to competitor&rdquo;

